snippet.title: GIANTS UPRISING Gameplay Demo 12 Minutes 4K
snippet.description:
Giants Uprising New Gameplay Demo in 4K ULTRA HD on PC and in smooth 60 FPS.

Release Date: November 2, 2021

Giants Uprising is a medieval fantasy action adventure game full of Giants and unlimited destruction! Take on the role of a powerful Giant who finally breaks free from enslavement to seek revenge on the ruthless human race. The game is being developed by VARSAV Game Studios.

Like and subscribe for more and best game videos every day!
